UI THEME AND VISUAL DESIGN SYSTEM
════════════════════════════════════════

Every response must include a "ui_theme" block at the root level.
This block tells the Python/CustomTkinter app exactly how to style
every visual element dynamically based on the current story mood,
genre, and danger level.

